extendedInfo.description: Astrological calculator for professional astrologers.The calculator will provide you with the following data:Strict coordinates of planets, stars, asteroids and fictitious planets:Real planets: Moon, Sun, Mercury, Venus, Mars, Jupiter, Saturn, Uranus, Neptune, Pluto.Other spase bodies: Adams, Admetos, Apollon, Chiron, Cupido, Drahma, Hades, Harrington, Iris, Kronos, Leverrier, Lowell, Mean Node, Nibiru, Pickering, Poseidon, Proserpina, True Node, Vulkanus, Vulkan, Waldemath, White Moon, Zeus, Mean Apogee, Osc. Apogee, Intp. Apogee, Intp. Perigee.House systems: Placidus, Koch, Porphyrius, Regiomontanus, Campanus, Equal, Vehlow equal, Meridian houses, Azimuthal (horizontal) system, Polich/Page (topocentric) system, Alcabitius.The calculator will also show coordinates of cusps of all twelve houses, as well as Ascendant, MC, ARMC (sidereal time), Vertex, Equatorial Ascendant, Co-Ascendant (Koch and Munkasey interpretations), Polar Ascendant.The following options are available:Show heliocentric positions, true or apparent positions, equatorial positions, topocentric positions, sidereal positions, cartesian or polar coordinates, positions in international celestial reference system.Consider precession, nutation, gravitational deflection, annual aberration of light.This is demo version. It shows coordinates of 5 planets and 5 cusps of houses.Other tags: Aries, Taurus, Gemini, Cancer, Leo, Virgo, Libra, Scorpio, Sagittarius, Capricorn, Aquarius, Pisces.
